  <nav class="nav" id="nav"><div class="container nav-inner"><a class="brand" href="#top"><span class="mark"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 17c-2.8-1.8-7-4.8-7-8.2A3.8 3.8 0 0 1 8.8 5c1.4 0 2.5.7 3.2 1.8A3.8 3.8 0 0 1 15.2 5 3.8 3.8 0 0 1 19 8.8c0 3.4-4.2 6.4-7 8.2Z" fill="white"/></svg></span><span>Pawhaven Club<small>Pet hotel, grooming & concierge</small></span></a><div class="nav-links"><a href="#services">Services</a><a href="#experience">Experience</a><a href="#plans">Plans</a><a href="#booking">Book</a><a href="#reviews">Reviews</a></div><div class="nav-actions"><a class="btn btn-outline" href="tel:+6186240555">Call</a><a class="btn btn-primary" href="#booking">Book Visit</a></div></div></nav>

  <main id="top">
    <header class="hero"><div class="hero-photo"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Premium pet services reception with dog and cat"></div><div class="paw one"></div><div class="paw two"></div><div class="container hero-grid"><div><div class="eyebrow">Luxury grooming · Daycare · Boarding · Walks · Training</div><h1 class="split"><span>A private club</span><span>for pets with</span><span>particular people.</span></h1><p class="lead reveal">A sophisticated pet services website designed to sell trust: concierge intake, calm handling, spotless facilities, membership-style care and seamless booking for discerning pet parents.</p><div class="hero-actions reveal"><a class="btn btn-light" href="#booking">Book a Temperament Visit</a><a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#services">Explore Services</a><a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:+6186240555">Click to Call</a></div><div class="trust-row reveal"><div class="trust"><b>4.9★</b><span>Pet parent rating</span></div><div class="trust"><b>24/7</b><span>Stay updates</span></div><div class="trust"><b>6</b><span>Care pathways</span></div><div class="trust"><b>1:1</b><span>Care profiles</span></div></div></div><aside class="hero-card reveal"><div class="status"><span class="pulse"></span> Concierge bookings open</div><h3>Start with the right care path.</h3><p>Tell us about your pet’s temperament, routine and care needs so every visit begins calmly.</p><div class="mini-book"><select id="quickType"><option>New pet temperament visit</option><option>Grooming appointment</option><option>Daycare trial day</option><option>Boarding stay</option><option>Dog walking plan</option><option>Training consultation</option></select><input placeholder="Pet name, breed or preferred date"><a class="btn btn-light" id="quickBook" href="#booking">Start Booking</a></div></aside></div></header>
    <div class="rail"><div class="rail-track"><span>Temperament-led care</span><span>Luxury grooming suites</span><span>Private boarding rooms</span><span>Supervised playgroups</span><span>Daily photo updates</span><span>Pet parent concierge</span><span>Temperament-led care</span><span>Luxury grooming suites</span><span>Private boarding rooms</span><span>Supervised playgroups</span><span>Daily photo updates</span><span>Pet parent concierge</span></div></div>
    <section class="photo-strip"><div class="container strip-grid"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Luxury pet concierge reception"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Luxury dog grooming salon"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Premium dog daycare"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Luxury cat boarding suite"></div></section>

    <section class="concierge"><div class="container concierge-grid"><article class="editorial-card reveal"><div class="eyebrow">Luxury pet hospitality</div><h2>Built for the questions pet parents ask before they book.</h2><p>Pawhaven Club balances warmth with operational confidence. The layout reassures visitors around cleanliness, safety, staff supervision, temperament matching, updates, pricing and next steps — the details that convert a cautious pet parent into a booking.</p><div class="metric-grid"><div class="metric"><b class="counter" data-target="96">0</b><span>Premium UX score</span></div><div class="metric"><b class="counter" data-target="6">0</b><span>Service categories</span></div><div class="metric"><b class="counter" data-target="24">0</b><span>Hour update rhythm</span></div></div></article><div class="detail-stack"><figure class="media-card large reveal tilt"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Luxury pet concierge reception"><b>Concierge arrival.</b></figure><div class="detail-pair"><figure class="media-card small reveal tilt"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Luxury cat boarding suite"><b>Quiet cat suites.</b></figure><figure class="media-card small reveal tilt"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Dog after luxury grooming bath"><b>Spa-level finish.</b></figure></div></div></div></section><div class="divider"></div>

    <section class="services" id="services"><div class="container"><div class="section-head reveal"><div><div class="eyebrow">Complete pet services</div><h2>Everything a pet parent looks for, presented with polish.</h2></div><p>Each service card explains the offer, signals safety and routes directly into the booking form with the right appointment type pre-selected.</p></div><div class="cards"><article class="card reveal" data-service="Grooming appointment"><div class="icon">✂</div><h3>Grooming Spa</h3><p>Bathing, brushing, breed-aware trims, nail care, de-shedding and calm handling for sensitive pets.</p><div class="tags"><span class="tag">Spa bath</span><span class="tag">De-shed</span><span class="tag">Nails</span></div></article><article class="card reveal" data-service="Daycare trial day"><div class="icon">☀</div><h3>Daycare</h3><p>Supervised playgroups, rest periods, enrichment activities and temperament-matched social time.</p><div class="tags"><span class="tag">Playgroups</span><span class="tag">Enrichment</span><span class="tag">Updates</span></div></article><article class="card reveal" data-service="Boarding stay"><div class="icon">◒</div><h3>Boarding Hotel</h3><p>Private suites, bedtime routines, feeding notes, comfort items and daily check-ins while you travel.</p><div class="tags"><span class="tag">Private suites</span><span class="tag">Daily photos</span><span class="tag">Routine care</span></div></article><article class="card reveal" data-service="Dog walking plan"><div class="icon">↗</div><h3>Dog Walking</h3><p>Neighbourhood walks, solo walks, small-group walks and GPS-style visit summaries for peace of mind.</p><div class="tags"><span class="tag">Solo</span><span class="tag">Group</span><span class="tag">Scheduled</span></div></article><article class="card reveal" data-service="Training consultation"><div class="icon">◎</div><h3>Training</h3><p>Puppy foundations, leash manners, recall, confidence building and practical home routines.</p><div class="tags"><span class="tag">Puppy</span><span class="tag">Manners</span><span class="tag">Confidence</span></div></article><article class="card reveal" data-service="Pet wellness check"><div class="icon">♡</div><h3>Wellness Checks</h3><p>Coat, skin, ear, dental, weight and comfort observations with referral guidance when needed.</p><div class="tags"><span class="tag">Observation</span><span class="tag">Care notes</span><span class="tag">Referral-ready</span></div></article></div></div></section>

    <section class="visual" id="experience"><div class="spotlight"></div><div class="container"><div class="section-head reveal"><div><div class="eyebrow">Premium pet experience</div><h2>Designed to reassure humans and delight pets.</h2></div><p>Strong pet service websites need more than cute photos. They must communicate cleanliness, safety, temperament awareness, supervision and trust.</p></div><div class="image-grid"><figure class="media-card gallery-main reveal tilt"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Luxury dog grooming salon"><figcaption class="caption"><b>Grooming with calm handling.</b><span>Clean suites, gentle technique and breed-aware finishing.</span></figcaption></figure><div class="image-stack"><figure class="media-card gallery-small reveal tilt"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Premium dog daycare"><figcaption class="caption"><b>Supervised play.</b><span>Safe groups, enrichment and structured rest.</span></figcaption></figure><figure class="media-card gallery-small reveal tilt"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Premium dog training studio"><figcaption class="caption"><b>Training with confidence.</b><span>Practical routines for puppies, manners and recall.</span></figcaption></figure></div></div></div></section>

    <section class="protocol"><div class="container"><div class="section-head reveal"><div><div class="eyebrow">Safety & trust architecture</div><h2>Premium means operationally excellent.</h2></div><p>This section adds the proof high-value pet parents need before leaving a beloved animal in someone else’s care.</p></div><div class="protocol-grid"><article class="protocol-item reveal"><div class="count">01</div><h3>Temperament matching</h3><p>Pets are grouped by energy, confidence and social style — not simply by size.</p></article><article class="protocol-item reveal"><div class="count">02</div><h3>Cleanliness rhythm</h3><p>Suites, grooming surfaces and play zones follow a documented reset schedule.</p></article><article class="protocol-item reveal"><div class="count">03</div><h3>Human supervision</h3><p>Daycare and boarding are presented as guided care, not unattended holding.</p></article><article class="protocol-item reveal"><div class="count">04</div><h3>Owner updates</h3><p>Photo notes, feeding observations and pickup summaries remove uncertainty.</p></article></div></div></section>

    <section class="membership" id="plans"><div class="container membership-grid"><article class="editorial-card reveal"><div class="eyebrow">Membership-style care</div><h2>Recurring care, without the recurring stress.</h2><p>Turn one-off bookings into predictable revenue with polished membership plans for grooming, daycare, walking and boarding add-ons.</p><div class="metric-grid"><div class="metric"><b class="counter" data-target="3">0</b><span>Membership tiers</span></div><div class="metric"><b class="counter" data-target="7">0</b><span>Day care rhythm</span></div><div class="metric"><b class="counter" data-target="1">0</b><span>Pet profile</span></div></div></article><div class="plans"><article class="plan reveal"><div class="plan-top"><div><h3>Essential Care</h3><p>For regular grooming, walks and simple recurring appointments.</p></div><div class="price">$49</div></div><ul><li>Priority appointment windows</li><li>Pet profile and care notes</li><li>Monthly wellness observations</li></ul></article><article class="plan featured reveal"><div class="plan-top"><div><h3>Social Club</h3><p>For daycare pets who thrive with supervised play and routine.</p></div><div class="price">$129</div></div><ul><li>Weekly daycare booking</li><li>Photo updates and enrichment notes</li><li>Member grooming savings</li></ul></article><article class="plan reveal"><div class="plan-top"><div><h3>Concierge Stay</h3><p>For travel periods, overnight boarding and high-touch care.</p></div><div class="price">Custom</div></div><ul><li>Boarding suite priority</li><li>Feeding and medication notes</li><li>Daily update package</li></ul></article></div></div></section>

    <section class="journey"><div class="container journey-grid"><figure class="media-card tall reveal tilt"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Pet wellness consultation"></figure><div class="reveal"><div class="eyebrow">Care journey</div><h2 style="margin:16px 0 24px">From first booking to happy pickup.</h2><div class="steps"><div class="step"><div class="num">1</div><p><b>Pet profile</b>Capture temperament, health notes, feeding, medication, favourite comforts and handling preferences.</p></div><div class="step"><div class="num">2</div><p><b>Arrival and settling</b>Staff welcome your pet calmly and place them into the right care path, suite or playgroup.</p></div><div class="step"><div class="num">3</div><p><b>Care with updates</b>Photo notes, enrichment details and observations keep pet parents informed without needing to call.</p></div><div class="step"><div class="num">4</div><p><b>Pickup summary</b>Share grooming notes, behaviour highlights, wellness observations and recommended next visit.</p></div></div></div></div></section>

    <section class="booking-section" id="booking"><div class="container booking-grid"><div class="reveal"><div class="eyebrow">Appointments</div><h2 style="margin:16px 0 22px">Make every booking feel personal.</h2><p>The booking block is designed for pet service software, online forms, grooming calendars, boarding enquiries or a custom booking workflow.</p><div class="features"><span>Vaccination notes</span><span>Temperament profile</span><span>Feeding routine</span><span>Photo updates</span></div></div><div class="booking-card reveal"><form id="bookingForm"><div class="field"><label>Pet name</label><input placeholder="Luna"></div><div class="field"><label>Pet type</label><select><option>Dog</option><option>Cat</option><option>Small animal</option><option>Multiple pets</option></select></div><div class="field"><label>Breed / size</label><input placeholder="Cavoodle, medium"></div><div class="field"><label>Age</label><input placeholder="3 years"></div><div class="field full"><label>Service needed</label><select id="serviceSelect"><option>New pet temperament visit</option><option>Grooming appointment</option><option>Daycare trial day</option><option>Boarding stay</option><option>Dog walking plan</option><option>Training consultation</option><option>Pet wellness check</option><option>Pet taxi enquiry</option></select></div><div class="field"><label>Preferred date</label><input type="date"></div><div class="field"><label>Preferred time</label><select><option>Morning</option><option>Midday</option><option>Afternoon</option><option>First available</option></select></div><div class="field"><label>Your name</label><input placeholder="Pet parent name"></div><div class="field"><label>Phone</label><input placeholder="Your phone"></div><div class="field full"><label>Care notes</label><textarea placeholder="Temperament, allergies, feeding, medication, grooming preferences or boarding dates."></textarea></div><div class="notice" id="notice">For urgent veterinary symptoms or emergencies, contact a veterinary clinic immediately. Pawhaven care notes are for service planning only.</div><div class="form-actions"><button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Request Booking</button><a class="btn btn-outline" href="tel:+6186240555">Call Concierge</a></div><div class="confirm" id="confirm">Your request has been received. The Pawhaven team will confirm availability and care details shortly.</div></form></div></div></section>

    <section class="reviews" id="reviews"><div class="container"><div class="section-head reveal"><div><div class="eyebrow">Pet parent confidence</div><h2>Trust signals that make booking easier.</h2></div><p>Reviews highlight safety, communication, cleanliness, temperament awareness and how pets behave at pickup.</p></div><div class="review-wrap reveal"><div class="review-grid" id="reviewGrid"><article class="review"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p>“The daycare updates are thoughtful and our dog comes home happy, calm and ready for dinner.”</p><b>Emily R. · Dog parent</b></article><article class="review"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p>“The grooming appointment felt calm from start to finish. They asked about sensitivities before touching him.”</p><b>Marcus P. · Grooming client</b></article><article class="review"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p>“Boarding was spotless, organised and reassuring. The photo updates made our trip so much easier.”</p><b>Sienna L. · Boarding guest</b></article><article class="review"><div class="stars">★★★★★</div><p>“Our nervous rescue was matched with the right group. The team clearly understood dogs.”</p><b>Jules K. · Daycare member</b></article></div><div class="review-controls"><button class="circle-btn" id="prevReview">←</button><button class="circle-btn" id="nextReview">→</button></div></div></div></section>

    <section class="faq"><div class="container faq-grid"><div class="reveal"><div class="eyebrow">Questions before booking</div><h2 style="margin:16px 0 22px">Answer hesitation before it becomes a lost enquiry.</h2><p>Premium service pages should remove friction by answering practical concerns clearly.</p></div><div class="accordion reveal"><div class="faq-item open"><button class="faq-q">Do you require a trial day before daycare? <span>+</span></button><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. New daycare guests begin with a temperament visit so we can understand confidence, play style and handling preferences.</p></div></div><div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Can you manage feeding and medication notes? <span>+</span></button><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. The intake form captures feeding routines, medication instructions and comfort items for boarding and extended care.</p></div></div><div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Will I receive updates during boarding? <span>+</span></button><div class="faq-a"><p>Boarding guests can receive photo updates, feeding notes and a pickup summary depending on the care package selected.</p></div></div><div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Do you groom anxious pets? <span>+</span></button><div class="faq-a"><p>We use calm handling and may recommend shorter introductory appointments for pets who need a slower grooming plan.</p></div></div></div></div></section>

    <section class="final"><div class="final-photo"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Premium boarding suite"></div><div class="container reveal"><div class="eyebrow">Premium pet services demo</div><h2>Everything a modern pet care brand needs to turn trust into bookings.</h2><p>Pawhaven Club includes cinematic imagery, concierge positioning, safety protocols, memberships, reviews carousel, FAQ, mobile CTAs, intake-focused booking and sophisticated animation.</p><div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center"><a class="btn btn-light" href="#booking">Book a Visit</a><a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:+6186240555">Call the Club</a></div></div></section>
